edu.kit.joana.ifc.sdg.util.sdg

Interface SDGNodePredicate

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultSDGNodePredicate

    public interface SDGNodePredicate
    An SDGNodePredicate decides by some magic criterion, whether a given sdg node is 'interesting'. This is needed for the construction of a reduced control-flow graph. The ReducedCFGBuilder can be configured using a custom SDGNodePredicate to support different reduced views of a control-flow graph.
    Author:
    Martin Mohr
